Package: simplefmi
Type: Package
Title: An R package for FMI weather data
Version: 0.1.1
Author: Markus Paasiniemi [aut]
Maintainer: Markus Paasiniemi <paasim@iki.fi>
Description: A simplified version of the amazing fmi-package for downloading weather data via FMI API in a tidy format. Requires personal fmi-apikey.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0.2)
Imports:
    curl,
    dplyr,
    lubridate,
    magrittr,
    stringr,
    tibble,
    tidyr
Encoding: UTF-8
